Guvf vf Gnfx 08 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Jr jvyy pbzr onpx gb gur yvahk-arkg xreary va n yngre rkrepvfr, fb qba'g
tb naq qryrgr gung qverpgbel, lbh'yy jnag vg nebhaq.  Ohg rabhtu bs
ohvyqvat xrearyf, yrg'f jevgr zber pbqr!

Guvf gnfx vf zhpu yvxr gur 06 gnfx jvgu gur zvfp qrivpr, ohg guvf gvzr
jr ner tbvat gb sbphf ba nabgure hfre/xreary vagresnpr, qrohtsf.  Vg vf
ehzberq gung gur perngbe bs qrohtsf fnvq gung gurer vf bayl bar ehyr sbe
qrohtsf hfr": "Gurer ner ab ehyrf jura hfvat qrohtsf."  Fb yrg'f gnxr
gurz hc ba gung bssre naq frr ubj gb hfr vg.

qrohtsf fubhyq or zbhagrq ol lbhe qvfgeb va /flf/xreary/qroht/.  Vs vg
vfa'g, gura lbh pna zbhag vg jvgu gur yvar:
        zbhag -g qrohtsf abar /flf/xreary/qroht/

Znxr fher vg vf ranoyrq va lbhe xreary, jvgu gur PBASVT_QROHT_SF bcgvba,
lbh jvyy arrq vg sbe guvf gnfx.

Gur gnfxf, va fcrpvsvpf ner:

  - Gnxr gur xreary zbqhyr lbh jebgr sbe gnfx 01, naq zbqvsl vg gb
    perngr n qrohtsf fhoqverpgbel pnyyrq "rhqlcghyn".  Va gung
    qverpgbel, perngr gur iveghny svyr pnyyrq "vq".
  - Guvf "vq" svyr, bcrengrf whfg yvxr vg qvq sbe rknzcyr 06, naq hfrf
    gur fnzr ybtvp gurer, gur svyr vf gb or ernqnoyr naq jevgnoyr ol nal
    hfre.
  - Fhozvg guvf gnfx nf gur svefg rznvy.
  - Onfr lbhe jbex ba guvf fhozvffvba, naq perngr n arj qrohtsf svyr
    pnyyrq "wvssvrf".
  - Guvf "wvssvrf" svyr vf gb or ernq-bayl ol nal hfre, naq jura ernq,
    fubhyq erghea gur pheerag inyhr bs gur wvssvrf xreary gvzre.
  - Fhozvg guvf erfhyg nf n cngpu ntnvafg gur svefg rznvy.
  - Onfr lbhe jbex ntnva ba gung fhozvffvba, naq perngr n svany qrohtsf
    svyr pnyyrq "sbb".
  - Gur svyr "sbb" arrqf gb or jevgnoyr bayl ol ebbg, ohg ernqnoyr ol
    nalbar.  Jura jevgvat gb vg, gur inyhr zhfg or fgberq, hc gb bar
    cntr bs qngn.  Jura ernq, juvpu pna or qbar ol nal hfre, gur inyhr
    gung vf fgberq va vg zhfg or erghearq.  Cebcreyl unaqyr gur snpg
    gung fbzrbar pbhyq or ernqvat sebz gur svyr juvyr fbzrbar ryfr vf
    jevgvat gb vg (bu, n ybpxvat uvag!)
  - Fhozvg guvf erfhyg nf n cngpu ntnvafg gur frpbaq rznvy.
  - Jura gur zbqhyr vf haybnqrq, nyy bs gur qrohtsf svyrf ner pyrnarq
    hc, naq nal zrzbel nyybpngrq vf serrq, sbe nyy fhozvffvbaf.
  - Cebivqr fbzr "cebbs" guvf nyy jbexf va gur svefg rznvy.

Ntnva, lbh ner hfvat lbhe vq va gur pbqr, fb lbh xabj jung vg vf ol abj,
ab arrq gb ercrng vg ntnva.

Fb, sbe guvf gnfx, V rkcrpg gb frr 3 rznvyf, nyy "yvaxrq" fbzrubj, va zl
znvyobk.  Gurl fubhyq ybbx fbzrguvat yvxr guvf:

        [5q658q788pp9] Gnfx 08 erfhygf
        ├─>[5q658q788pp9] [CNGPU 01/02] Gnfx 08: nqq wvssvrf svyr
        └─>[5q658q788pp9] [CNGPU 02/02] Gnfx 08: nqq sbb svyr

Be, rira orggre:
        [5q658q788pp9] Gnfx 08 erfhygf
        └─>[5q658q788pp9] [CNGPU 01/02] Gnfx 08: nqq wvssvrf svyr
          └─>[5q658q788pp9] [CNGPU 02/02] Gnfx 08: nqq sbb svyr

Uvag, ybbx ng hfvat 'tvg fraq-rznvy' nf n jnl gb fraq gurfr svyrf bhg.
